@page "/services"

<h2 class="mb-4">Our Services</h2>
<p class="card-text">"At all times, we adhere to and advocate for the highest industry-specific best practices across every segment we serve. By aligning our solutions with proven standards and evolving benchmarks, we ensure our clients receive not only cutting-edge innovation but also dependable, compliant, and future-ready results. Our commitment to best practices is not just a box we check, it's a foundation for delivering consistent excellence, minimizing risk, and building long-term value in every engagement."</p>
<h4>Software Development</h4>
<div class="services row g-4">
    <!-- Core Services -->
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">API & Backend Development</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Design and build robust secure APIs and microservices, event driven designs, scalable architectures, and performance optimization. Includes monitoring and logging, RESTful APIs, and integration with Azure services.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">.NET & Blazor Development</h5>
                <p class="card-text">End-to-end web application development using the latest stable versions of C#, .NET, and Blazor technologies. Includes responsive UI, secure data transfer, and flexible hosting.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Azure Cloud Development</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Develop code that runs in serverless architectures that is scalable, resilient, secure, and designed to reduce overall maintenance costs.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Training & Knowledge Transfer </h5>
                <p class="card-text">Hands-on workshops and mentoring in .NET, Azure, and DevOps to upskill internal teams and ensure self-sufficiency post-engagement.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h4>Networking and Site Reliability</h4>
<div class="services row g-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">DevOps & CI/CD Automation</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Implement CI/CD practices with GitHub Actions or Azure DevOps and Infrastructure-as-Code (ARM, Bicep, Terraform). Automate builds, tests, code scanning, and deployments for reliability and speed.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Disaster Recovery & Resiliency </h5>
                <p class="card-text">Develop BCDR plans, configure geo-redundancy and automated backups in Azure to ensure business continuity.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Site Reliability Engineering</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Apply SRE best practices: monitoring, alerting, SLO/SLI definition, incident response automation, and chaos testing to improve system uptime and performance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Site Surveys & Technical Assessments</h5>
                <p class="card-text">On-site and remote assessments for small orgs (under 100 employees) covering network, security, and infrastructure, with actionable improvement plans.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h4>Modernization and Cloud Migrations</h4>
<div class="services row g-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Azure Cloud Architecture & Migrations</h5>
                <p class="card-text">Design and execute lift-and-shift or refactoring migrations for organizations up to 300 employees. Provision Azure VMs, App Services, Azure SQL, and implement scalable cloud solutions.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Cloud Cost Optimization </h5>
                <p class="card-text">Analyze Azure deployments for cost inefficiencies, recommend reserved instances, rightsizing, and auto-scaling strategies to minimize expenses.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h4>Compliance</h4>
<div class="services row g-4">
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Security & Compliance </h5>
                <p class="card-text">Conduct security audits, implement Azure security best practices (Entra ID, Key Vault), and assist with SOC 2 or HIPAA compliance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="card h-100 border-primary">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">SOX and HIPAA Compliance </h5>
                <p class="card-text">Familiarity with common industry standards and the systems and processes required to maintain compliance.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
